            <li><strong>Schedule Service:</strong> Call or book online for same-day or next-day appointments</li>
            <li><strong>Thorough Diagnosis:</strong> We test all system components to identify the root cause</li>
            <li><strong>Upfront Quote:</strong> We explain the problem and provide pricing before repairs</li>
            <li><strong>Expert Repair:</strong> Quality repairs using OEM or equivalent parts</li>
            <li><strong>System Test:</strong> We verify proper operation in both heating and cooling modes</li>
            <li><strong>Recommendations:</strong> Tips to prevent future problems</li>
          </ol>

          <h2>Heat Pump Repair vs. Replacement</h2>
          <p>We provide honest recommendations based on your specific situation:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Repair:</strong> Usually the best choice for systems under 10 years old with minor issues</li>
            <li><strong>Consider Replacement:</strong> If repair costs exceed 50% of a new system's cost</li>
            <li><strong>Replace:</strong> For units over 15 years old or those needing frequent major repairs</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We'll explain all your options and never pressure you into an unnecessary replacement.</p>

